      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S NOWHERE (7) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a one length second over 450m at this track, clocking 25.63. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Likely to feature again. THOR LEGEND (3) jumped well and was a winner (25.57) two back from a tricky draw then last start drew a squeeze box again but got further back and finished 7th at this track (26.78). Expected to give a good account. GRAVY TRAIN (8) has gone well at his last couple of runs here, most recently when third beaten 3 lengths (25.87). The form out of last run is most impressive. Ready to find winning form. PRICKLE (5) has claims fresh from a recent placing at big odds.",
